@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
participant Bot
participant CometD
participant Telegram
participant User

Bot -> CometD: /meta/handshake
CometD --> Bot: clientId + cookie
Bot -> CometD: /meta/subscribe (per branch prefix)
Bot -> CometD: /events/INIT (per branch prefix)
loop long-poll
  Bot -> CometD: /meta/connect
  CometD --> Bot: events/meta
end
CometD --> Bot: VISIT_CALL(TelegramCustomerId)
Bot -> Bot: validate branch subscription
Bot -> Telegram: send_message()
Telegram --> User: called to service point
@enduml
